classDiagram
    title Chapter 17: Anyhow and Thiserror
    
    class Anyhow {
        <<crate>>
        +Result~T~
        +anyhow!()
        +context()
        +bail!()
    }
    
    class Thiserror {
        <<crate>>
        +~thiserror~
        +~error~ derive
        +Display impl
    }
    
    class AppError {
        +IO errors
        +Parse errors
        +Custom errors
    }
    
    Anyhow --> AppError : For application layer
    Thiserror --> AppError : For library errors
    
    Note over Anyhow: Quick error handling\nDynamic error types
    Note over Thiserror: Compile-time errors\nStatic error types
